<figure id="CNX_Calc_Figure_16_01_004">
<media id="fs-id1167793929139" alt="A visual representation of the given vector field in a coordinate plane with two additional diagrams with notation. The first representation shows the vector field. The arrows are circling the origin in a clockwise motion. The second representation shows concentric circles, highlighting the radial pattern. The The third representation shows the concentric circles. It also shows arrows for the radial vector &lt;a,b> for all points (a,b). Each is perpendicular to the arrows in the given vector field.">
