<exercise id="fs-id1167793584551">
<problem id="fs-id1167793584553">
<media id="fs-id1167794288058" alt="A visual representation of a vector field in two dimensions. The arrows are larger the further away from the origin they are. They stretch out and away from the origin in a radial pattern.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Calc_Figure_16_01_214.jpg"/>
