</exercise>
<para id="fs-id1167794288083">For the following exercises, let <m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>F</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>i</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>j</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>G</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>−</m:mtext><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>i</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>j</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> and <m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>H</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>i</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>–</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>j</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> Match the vector fields with their graphs in <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>I</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mtext>IV</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para><list id="fs-id1167794223613" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item><m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>F</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>G</m:mtext></m:mstyle></m:mrow></m:math></item>
<item><m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>F</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>H</m:mtext></m:mstyle></m:mrow></m:math></item>
<item><m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>G</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>H</m:mtext></m:mstyle></m:mrow></m:math></item>
<item><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>−</m:mtext><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>F</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>G</m:mtext></m:mstyle></m:mrow></m:math></item>
</list>
