<media id="fs-id1167794076412" alt="A visual representation of a vector field in two dimensions. The arrows are larger the further away from y axis they are. The arrows are pointing out from the origin in a spiral shape. In quadrant 1, the arrows are more vertical and curve up. In quadrant 2, the arrows are more horizontal and curve down. In quadrant 3, the arrows are more vertical and curve down. In quadrant 4, the arrows are more horizontal and curve up. Each quadrant’s arrows merge into the two on either side of it.">
